commit.message: Corrected some minor typos in code gen

Added session save (file download and re-upload to restore the same setup).

Added support for access modifiers for data members and methods (public, protected, private).

Added support for object inheritance with full interface.
Added ability to add class constructor/declaration to main file through button click.
added more calls to refresh of files
Switched the function body editor text area content from placeholder to value
Added edit and delete of classes/names
